data.description: Beautiful historic home located in the heart of Eastern Rowan County ready for you to make yours!  This home has 2,798 sf, 4 BRs, 2.5 baths and sits on 2.13 acres!  Caught your eye yet?  Come enjoy morning coffee on your front porch or have a lazy afternoon entertaining on your 530 sf deck with it's own sand box!  Home has large living, dining and kitchen areas! Spacious kitchen offers large island and lots of cabinetry.  Walk in pantry even offers a can organizer!  Master is on main-offers updated bath with walk in closet!  Cubby going to exterior deck is perfect for organizing! Additional office/sun room area can be used as storage or another place to relax.  Take the grand stairs up to the upper level where you'll find oversized bedrooms/office/flex space and another bathroom! Exterior has well house/well is used for irrigation and two additional storage buildings w/power (both have concrete floors). Hardwood/tile/hardwood laminate flooring throughout-no carpet!  Security system!
